WEBVTT

01:37.860 --> 01:40.990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.090 --> 01:43.990
[Episode 10]

01:46.560 --> 01:48.200
Last time you asked me
to get two bottles of shampoo

01:48.200 --> 01:49.640
from two different places.

01:49.640 --> 01:51.240
What was the reason for that?

01:52.500 --> 01:53.680
At this moment,

01:53.789 --> 01:55.650
I can't tell you too many details.

01:55.870 --> 01:57.420
The whole story

01:57.440 --> 01:59.840
hasn't been investigated thoroughly yet.

02:00.920 --> 02:02.000
Then give me a sample.

02:02.000 --> 02:03.660
I'll help you investigate it.

02:05.460 --> 02:07.380
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

02:39.370 --> 02:42.600
[Shampoo]

02:46.130 --> 02:47.630
[Shampoo]

02:50.380 --> 02:52.730
[Search for Similar Items]

02:54.480 --> 02:55.420
[First-Tier Domestic Five-Star Hotel]

02:55.440 --> 02:56.630
[Exclusive Shampoo for Purong,
100% Authentic, Click Here If You Know]

03:06.930 --> 03:08.960
Mr. Ji, the test results are out.

03:09.240 --> 03:11.560
One of the bottles
is indeed a knockoff with fake labels.

03:11.560 --> 03:14.020
There are plenty of these
in the underground wholesale markets.

03:14.020 --> 03:15.020
Okay. Thank you.

03:21.600 --> 03:23.790
[Purong Shampoo]

03:26.070 --> 03:26.810
[Essential Oil Formula
Hotel Toiletries Set]

03:26.840 --> 03:27.620
[Deep Repair for a Healthy Glow]

03:27.660 --> 03:30.400
[First-Tier Domestic Five-Star Hotel,
Exclusive Shampoo for Purong]

03:40.760 --> 03:41.200
[Dear, the minimum wholesale
order quantity is 50 items in this shop.]

03:41.230 --> 03:41.740
[I am offline now. Please add PR12445.]

03:41.760 --> 03:42.360
[I'll reply once I see your messages.]

03:46.860 --> 03:49.910
[PR12445] [Search]

03:52.990 --> 03:55.280
[Purong Authentic Products Porter]

03:57.870 --> 03:58.860
[Purong Authentic Products Porter]

03:59.110 --> 04:01.560
[Conditioner] [Shower Gel]

04:03.830 --> 04:05.070
[Purong]

04:06.360 --> 04:09.650
[Shampoo]

04:12.270 --> 04:13.600
[Bad Review]

04:21.300 --> 04:22.200
[Shampoo]

04:22.320 --> 04:23.860
[Purong Authentic Products Porter]

04:39.000 --> 04:41.130
Okay. My treat tonight.

04:41.150 --> 04:43.150
Let's not go home until we're drunk.

04:45.350 --> 04:45.500
[Favorites]

04:45.640 --> 04:46.070
[Purong Authentic Products Porter]

04:46.070 --> 04:48.580
[Send Message] [Audio/Video Call]

04:48.710 --> 04:50.250
[Shampoo]

04:54.330 --> 04:59.659
[Director's Office]

05:05.330 --> 05:06.390
What are you doing?

05:06.790 --> 05:07.850
What are you doing?

05:08.220 --> 05:09.160
I'm looking for my boss.

05:09.160 --> 05:10.160
What are you doing?

05:10.160 --> 05:11.510
I'm trying to stop you
from doing something stupid.

05:11.510 --> 05:13.120
I know what you've discovered.

05:13.120 --> 05:14.560
But now is not the time to report it yet.

05:14.560 --> 05:15.820
My time is running out.

05:15.870 --> 05:17.830
Now I have three bad reviews.

05:17.830 --> 05:19.980
Zhang Cailu
has already talked about firing me.

05:19.980 --> 05:21.010
Zhang Cailu?

05:21.800 --> 05:22.730
That forewoman?

05:26.240 --> 05:28.120
With this missing link adding to it,

05:28.120 --> 05:30.250
the whole story makes much more sense.

05:30.560 --> 05:33.230
Are you saying they are all in cahoots?

05:33.990 --> 05:35.350
I'm not sure yet.

05:36.000 --> 05:36.680
However,

05:37.240 --> 05:39.500
this industry chain
of reselling hotel supplies

05:39.500 --> 05:41.900
is too big for Zhang Cailu
to possess alone.

05:41.950 --> 05:43.830
She's just an underling at most.

05:44.810 --> 05:45.590
Things

05:46.070 --> 05:47.870
are not as simple as you thought.

05:49.870 --> 05:51.780
In my opinion,
you're also not as simple as I thought.

05:51.780 --> 05:53.270
You left Svelto Hotel Group behind

05:53.270 --> 05:54.830
and came all the way to Shanghai.

05:54.830 --> 05:56.360
You've stayed here for so long

05:56.360 --> 05:58.360
and meddled in so many things
that didn't concern you.

05:58.360 --> 05:59.930
What's your purpose here exactly?

05:59.930 --> 06:01.600
You're definitely not here
for sightseeing.

06:01.600 --> 06:02.970
You can't even protect yourself now.

06:02.970 --> 06:05.300
Yet you're still analyzing other people.

06:06.720 --> 06:09.250
Now Zhang Cailu is in the open
while you are in the dark.

06:09.250 --> 06:10.830
You know
she's trying to find fault with you,

06:10.830 --> 06:12.700
so just don't let her
get something on you anymore.

06:12.700 --> 06:13.220
Also,

06:13.510 --> 06:15.230
try to avoid reporting issues by bypassing

06:15.230 --> 06:17.360
your immediate supervisor like this.

06:18.090 --> 06:19.530
Just do your job well.

06:22.310 --> 06:24.510
What does it have to do with you?

06:34.940 --> 06:35.680
Miyu.

06:35.680 --> 06:36.720
I've been looking for you.

06:36.720 --> 06:37.580
Looking for me?

06:37.800 --> 06:39.460
Come with me to the Linen Room.

06:46.750 --> 06:47.950
I'm fired?

06:48.600 --> 06:49.270
Why?

06:49.480 --> 06:50.820
I don't want you to leave, either.

06:50.820 --> 06:52.720
But the assessment results are here.

06:52.720 --> 06:54.240
It can't be helped, Miyu.

06:54.560 --> 06:56.920
You are indeed
not very suitable to work in our hotel.

06:56.920 --> 06:57.720
Ms. Zhang,

06:58.600 --> 07:00.160
you know how I got

07:00.160 --> 07:01.160
these three bad reviews.

07:01.160 --> 07:02.190
What's more, didn't you say

07:02.190 --> 07:03.390
bad reviews would only affect bonuses?

07:03.390 --> 07:05.240
The situation is different now.

07:05.260 --> 07:06.950
The competition in every industry
is so intense

07:06.950 --> 07:08.600
that our hotel also has to

07:08.600 --> 07:09.800
enhance the requirements for employees.

07:09.800 --> 07:10.680
But

07:10.830 --> 07:12.360
this does not comply
with the dismissal process

07:12.360 --> 07:13.510
stated in the Hotel Staff Handbook.

07:13.510 --> 07:15.150
I'm just notifying you in advance

07:15.150 --> 07:16.750
so that you can be mentally prepared.

07:16.750 --> 07:18.190
The official notice will be issued soon.

07:18.190 --> 07:19.000
Ms. Zhang,

07:19.000 --> 07:21.260
the guest in Room 1801 is looking for you.

07:22.190 --> 07:23.000
Coming.

07:23.630 --> 07:24.750
Let's leave it at that for now.

07:24.750 --> 07:26.210
Just pack up and get ready.

07:30.160 --> 07:31.630
Xu Miyu, you really can't go in.

07:31.630 --> 07:33.040
-I'll just talk to Mr. Wei for 2 minutes.
-You can't do this.

07:33.040 --> 07:34.310
You need to make an appointment
to see Mr. Wei.

07:34.310 --> 07:34.920
Mr. Wei.

07:35.360 --> 07:36.240
I have some work-related matters

07:36.240 --> 07:37.270
to report to you.

07:39.680 --> 07:42.480
HSKP Department, Xu Miyu.

07:43.720 --> 07:44.920
You guys go first. I'll be right there.

07:44.920 --> 07:45.920
Okay, Mr. Wei.

07:47.000 --> 07:47.860
Come in with me.

07:50.450 --> 07:52.740
[Shampoo]

07:51.390 --> 07:53.000
The evidence you provided

07:53.000 --> 07:55.050
probably does not constitute direct proof.

07:55.050 --> 07:55.440
Here.

07:56.130 --> 08:01.020
[Purong Hotel]

07:58.360 --> 08:00.160
But as for the matters
you've reported to me,

08:00.160 --> 08:01.360
I'm aware of them now.

08:01.390 --> 08:03.120
I will personally investigate this case.

08:03.120 --> 08:04.580
No matter who is involved,

08:04.600 --> 08:05.600
I will investigate it to the end

08:05.600 --> 08:06.800
and show no leniency.

08:06.920 --> 08:09.650
Can I apply to
participate in the investigation?

08:11.050 --> 08:12.600
I advise you not to get involved

08:12.600 --> 08:13.510
in this matter.

08:13.920 --> 08:15.700
The more people are involved,
the more complicated it'll get.

08:15.700 --> 08:16.600
If Zhang Cailu

08:16.600 --> 08:17.900
and the people behind her
find out about this,

08:17.900 --> 08:19.850
it will not only be detrimental
to our subsequent investigation,

08:19.850 --> 08:21.120
but it might also bring you

08:21.120 --> 08:22.160
some unnecessary trouble.

08:22.160 --> 08:22.890
Understand?

08:24.130 --> 08:24.760
Okay.

08:25.560 --> 08:27.040
Xu Miyu, right?

08:30.160 --> 08:31.870
Thank you for telling me the information.

08:31.870 --> 08:33.789
As an employee of Purong Hotel,

08:33.820 --> 08:35.260
your sense of ownership

08:35.440 --> 08:36.909
and sense of responsibility for the hotel

08:36.909 --> 08:38.150
have truly impressed me.

08:38.150 --> 08:38.880
Don't worry.

08:39.200 --> 08:40.770
Leave this matter to me.

08:40.789 --> 08:42.150
Get back to work for now.

08:42.600 --> 08:45.330
I'll definitely give you
a satisfactory answer.

08:46.550 --> 08:47.610
Thank you, Mr. Wei.

08:59.480 --> 09:00.940
You don't need to come out.

09:01.190 --> 09:02.030
Xu Miyu.

09:02.390 --> 09:04.450
I am officially notifying you again.

09:04.720 --> 09:05.720
You are fired.

09:07.120 --> 09:08.720
Open your eyes and look carefully.

09:08.720 --> 09:10.600
It has the director's signature

09:10.600 --> 09:12.860
and the HR Department's official stamp.

09:13.150 --> 09:14.350
Stop making trouble.

09:16.980 --> 09:18.490
[Employment Termination Notice]

09:18.510 --> 09:21.010
[Feng Kaixin,
Director of the Customer Department]

09:33.420 --> 09:34.270
Mr. Ji.

09:35.360 --> 09:36.630
What happened?

09:38.740 --> 09:40.050
I'm leaving the hotel.

09:43.670 --> 09:44.790
So you reported it?

09:46.510 --> 09:48.820
Didn't I tell you
not to mess with Feng Kaixin?

09:48.820 --> 09:50.550
I didn't mess with Feng Kaixin.

09:52.750 --> 09:54.660
Zhang Cailu suddenly said
I would be fired.

09:54.660 --> 09:56.080
I really had no other choices,

09:56.080 --> 09:57.340
so I went to see Mr. Wei.

10:00.900 --> 10:02.640
Can I add you on WeChat?

10:02.660 --> 10:04.320
I still owe you 5,000 yuan.

10:05.360 --> 10:06.720
When I gather enough money,

10:06.720 --> 10:08.190
I'll transfer it to you on WeChat.

10:08.190 --> 10:10.000
We can talk about the money later.

10:10.000 --> 10:11.260
Have you appealed yet?

10:11.860 --> 10:12.780
Yes, I have.

10:14.090 --> 10:15.620
Before the results are out,

10:16.070 --> 10:17.360
I won't leave.

10:19.620 --> 10:20.800
But if...

10:22.000 --> 10:23.870
my appeal gets no result,

10:25.750 --> 10:28.280
where can I find you
to return the money to you?

10:28.870 --> 10:29.750
I'm right here.

10:30.260 --> 10:31.390
Will you always be here?

10:31.390 --> 10:32.520
I'll always be here.

10:53.640 --> 10:55.200
Why are you still coming here?

10:55.200 --> 10:56.860
Take off your uniform at once,

10:56.870 --> 10:58.960
return it to the Uniform Room,
and wrap things up.

10:58.960 --> 11:00.510
I still have a half-day shift to finish.

11:00.510 --> 11:01.750
Do you think you'll still get paid

11:01.750 --> 11:03.000
for this half-day shift?

11:03.000 --> 11:04.390
Whether I'll get paid or not,

11:04.390 --> 11:06.630
I'll finish the shift
which I'm supposed to finish.

11:06.630 --> 11:08.110
Ms. Zhang, the guest in Room 1812

11:08.110 --> 11:09.150
made a complaint.

11:10.240 --> 11:11.120
Got it.

11:17.800 --> 11:19.460
[Appeal Submitted, Pending Review]

11:29.920 --> 11:31.990
[Appeal Submitted, Pending Review]

11:48.870 --> 11:49.720
Miyu.

11:50.530 --> 11:51.890
Why don't you wait a bit longer?

11:51.890 --> 11:53.810
Black Card Ji
is making a complaint right now.

11:53.810 --> 11:55.630
It's driving Zhang Cailu crazy.

11:56.150 --> 11:58.410
Do you know what he's complaining about?

11:58.920 --> 11:59.830
The shampoo.

12:02.240 --> 12:02.870
Is that so?

12:03.670 --> 12:05.520
Ke also once told me that

12:05.550 --> 12:08.000
Zhang Cailu targetting you
had something to do with the shampoo,

12:08.000 --> 12:09.870
so don't be in a rush to leave now.

12:09.890 --> 12:10.890
Wait a bit longer.

12:10.920 --> 12:12.160
There might be hope.

12:19.900 --> 12:21.930
[HSKP Department, Xu Miyu]

12:27.350 --> 12:29.170
Complain... Let him complain.

12:30.070 --> 12:32.600
Just follow
the complaint handling process.

12:32.890 --> 12:34.510
Ask him to wait for us to handle it.

12:34.510 --> 12:35.510
I don't believe

12:35.510 --> 12:36.170
this matter

12:36.430 --> 12:37.750
won't cool down in three days.

12:37.750 --> 12:40.630
Mr. Feng, this complaint hit the bullseye.

12:41.010 --> 12:42.470
The guest has a black card,

12:42.470 --> 12:43.670
so he's very powerful.

12:43.670 --> 12:45.640
I'm afraid I'm no match for him.

12:45.670 --> 12:48.950
He's Ji Feng,
and I've had a drink with him before.

12:49.360 --> 12:50.960
What's there to be afraid of?

12:51.240 --> 12:52.960
Besides, no matter how powerful he is,

12:52.960 --> 12:54.080
he's just a guest.

12:54.280 --> 12:56.310
Is he going to stay at the hotel

12:56.340 --> 12:58.340
until the result comes out?

12:59.630 --> 13:00.960
Let me teach you a trick.

13:01.020 --> 13:02.270
If he is not satisfied,

13:02.270 --> 13:05.440
show him the list of fired employees.

13:05.650 --> 13:07.290
It's not that we didn't handle it.

13:07.290 --> 13:08.930
The rats have been caught.

13:09.080 --> 13:11.020
Then we can withdraw the fakes

13:11.520 --> 13:12.680
and leave the issue aside for a few days.

13:12.680 --> 13:14.880
This matter will blow over eventually.

13:15.170 --> 13:16.160
Yes.

13:16.230 --> 13:17.390
You're right.

13:17.440 --> 13:18.930
Settle it quickly.

13:19.240 --> 13:21.440
Can't you even solve such a small issue?

13:27.770 --> 13:28.810
[Aunt]

13:32.960 --> 13:33.750
Wei Siyuan.

13:35.080 --> 13:35.670
Aunt.

13:35.670 --> 13:38.600
Instead of
properly investigating the corruption,

13:38.750 --> 13:40.960
why did you fire an attendant?

13:41.510 --> 13:43.260
Being unable to solve the problem,

13:43.260 --> 13:45.720
you just dealt with the person
who raised it?

13:46.120 --> 13:48.270
Is this how you manage Purong Hotel?

13:48.640 --> 13:49.190
Well...

13:49.870 --> 13:51.060
Aunt, which matter are you talking about?

13:51.060 --> 13:52.390
I've heard about the matter

13:52.390 --> 13:54.070
of the executive floor.

13:54.150 --> 13:56.080
Are you still playing dumb with me?

13:56.120 --> 13:58.060
Aunt, please don't be angry.

13:58.090 --> 14:00.350
I really don't know anything about this.

14:00.360 --> 14:01.960
I-I'll go investigate it thoroughly.

14:01.960 --> 14:03.360
P-Please don't be angry.

14:03.360 --> 14:04.390
Within today,

14:04.750 --> 14:06.380
I want to see the investigation results.

14:06.380 --> 14:07.130
I'll be waiting.

14:07.130 --> 14:07.890
Okay.

14:23.000 --> 14:24.100
Feng Kaixin.

14:24.240 --> 14:26.510
Can you use your brain when you do things?

14:26.510 --> 14:27.750
You even made a big mess

14:27.750 --> 14:29.360
of such a trivial matter.

14:30.680 --> 14:31.740
I'm sorry, Mr. Wei.

14:31.870 --> 14:33.270
What are you talking about?

14:33.270 --> 14:35.120
Besides that shady business
in your HSKP Department,

14:35.120 --> 14:36.510
what else could it be?

14:36.510 --> 14:37.870
I asked you to handle it carefully.

14:37.870 --> 14:40.240
I didn't tell you to fire her.

14:42.510 --> 14:44.440
You mean Xu Miyu?

14:44.510 --> 14:45.510
I don't care what her name is.

14:45.510 --> 14:46.600
Let me tell you.

14:46.600 --> 14:48.360
Old Madam is now blaming me.

14:48.360 --> 14:49.270
What do you think I should do?

14:49.270 --> 14:50.840
T-T-This is impossible.

14:50.840 --> 14:52.720
I told the HR clerks to ask about it.

14:52.720 --> 14:54.260
She has no background.

14:54.280 --> 14:56.000
How did she get connected
with the chairwoman?

14:56.000 --> 14:57.000
Cut the crap.

14:57.000 --> 14:58.270
Give me a solution right now.

14:58.270 --> 15:00.200
Otherwise, just pack up and leave!

15:01.600 --> 15:02.660
What a useless man.

15:09.870 --> 15:11.520
Wu, find a resume for me.

15:11.750 --> 15:13.750
She's from the executive floor
of the HSKP Department.

15:13.750 --> 15:14.510
Xu...

15:15.720 --> 15:16.720
Xu Miyu.

15:16.880 --> 15:20.370
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

15:29.870 --> 15:31.360
According to the latest news,

15:31.360 --> 15:33.550
the complaint from Black Card Ji
has escalated.

15:33.550 --> 15:35.270
Even the chairwoman heard about it.

15:35.270 --> 15:36.870
There will be a good show
to watch this time.

15:36.870 --> 15:37.750
Miyu!

15:39.510 --> 15:40.720
It's good that you haven't left.

15:40.720 --> 15:43.150
Why didn't you tell me
about such a serious matter?

15:43.150 --> 15:44.750
It has nothing to do with you.

15:44.840 --> 15:46.360
I don't want to drag you into this.

15:46.360 --> 15:47.390
How would they dare?

15:47.390 --> 15:49.720
I would rip their skulls off
and make soup.

15:50.150 --> 15:50.720
Well...

15:51.020 --> 15:52.950
Are you planning to leave tonight?

15:53.150 --> 15:54.720
Stay at my place tonight.

15:54.740 --> 15:57.270
Tomorrow,
I'll go ask the HR clerks properly.

16:02.830 --> 16:03.830
[Notification:
Emergency Meeting for the Executive Floor]

16:03.000 --> 16:03.840
What's wrong?

16:03.850 --> 16:04.670
[Everyone should go to the meeting room
for a meeting in 30 minutes.]

16:03.960 --> 16:06.150
Emergency Meeting for the Executive Floor.

16:05.220 --> 16:05.870
[Feng Kaixin @ Xu Miyu]

16:06.870 --> 16:08.380
He even specifically tagged me.

16:08.380 --> 16:10.780
There's a sudden meeting
at this late hour?

16:10.960 --> 16:13.360
Why are we having a meeting
so late at night?

16:19.180 --> 16:19.900
Mr. Feng.

16:20.960 --> 16:21.750
Mr. Feng.

16:26.320 --> 16:27.120
Is everyone here?

16:27.120 --> 16:27.960
Yes.

16:28.660 --> 16:29.450
Okay.

16:30.270 --> 16:32.330
Since everyone is here, let's begin.

16:33.390 --> 16:36.000
I suddenly asked everyone
to have a meeting here tonight

16:36.000 --> 16:37.120
because I'm going to announce

16:37.120 --> 16:40.380
an important decision
for the hotel's personnel changes.

16:40.390 --> 16:43.750
As Zhang Cailu, the former forewoman
of the executive floor,

16:43.750 --> 16:45.880
violated work discipline seriously,

16:46.240 --> 16:48.870
which affected Purong Hotel's image
in the industry

16:48.870 --> 16:50.270
and among its customers,

16:50.270 --> 16:53.120
the hotel management
has unanimously decided

16:53.560 --> 16:55.750
to remove her from the position
of executive floor forewoman.

16:55.750 --> 16:56.630
Her dismissal

16:57.510 --> 16:58.670
is effective immediately.

16:58.670 --> 17:00.080
I'm fired?

17:00.360 --> 17:01.120
Mr. Feng,

17:01.360 --> 17:02.750
are you mistaken?

17:02.910 --> 17:05.970
This is a collective decision
by the hotel management.

17:07.760 --> 17:10.359
Do you think I'm making this up randomly?

17:11.160 --> 17:13.730
Then tell me what rules I've broken.

17:13.819 --> 17:15.079
Haven't I been doing everything

17:15.079 --> 17:17.540
according to the superiors' instructions?

17:17.670 --> 17:19.970
If you have any objection,
you can tell me after the meeting.

17:19.970 --> 17:21.880
But now I haven't finished speaking yet!

17:21.880 --> 17:22.829
Sit down!

17:35.270 --> 17:36.270
Let's continue.

17:39.270 --> 17:40.000
Next,

17:40.560 --> 17:42.880
I'm going to
announce a personnel appointment.

17:42.880 --> 17:44.110
From today onwards,

17:44.510 --> 17:46.570
the forewoman of the executive floor

17:46.850 --> 17:48.310
will be taken up by Xu Miyu.

17:52.020 --> 17:53.480
Congratulations, Ms. Xu.

18:02.350 --> 18:03.110
I hope

18:03.510 --> 18:06.840
from now on, you can lead everyone
to make progress together

18:07.110 --> 18:09.940
and improve the executive floor's work
to a higher level.

18:09.940 --> 18:10.450
Come on.

18:10.620 --> 18:12.560
Let's all give Ms. Xu

18:12.720 --> 18:14.960
a round of applause and cheer her on.

18:36.950 --> 18:37.880
-Mr. Ji.
-Hello.

18:38.510 --> 18:39.440
I'm Feng Kaixin.

18:39.610 --> 18:40.140
Mr. Feng.

18:40.960 --> 18:42.890
Our department
has just finished a meeting.

18:42.890 --> 18:45.680
Regarding the shampoo quality issue
you raised,

18:45.710 --> 18:46.800
we've punished

18:46.820 --> 18:48.610
the relevant personnel severely.

18:48.610 --> 18:49.610
Who was punished?

18:49.880 --> 18:50.720
Zhang Cailu,

18:51.010 --> 18:52.550
the forewoman of the executive floor.

18:52.550 --> 18:53.720
She has been fired.

18:54.470 --> 18:55.890
Sorry for the trouble, Mr. Feng.

18:55.890 --> 18:57.160
Please don't say that.

18:57.180 --> 19:00.360
Mr. Ji, you have a sharp eye.

19:00.380 --> 19:02.510
You helped our hotel get rid of a pest.

19:02.540 --> 19:04.370
We should be thanking you.

19:06.400 --> 19:07.680
To express our apologies,

19:07.680 --> 19:09.440
we've specially prepared this

19:09.460 --> 19:11.790
hotel toiletries gift box.

19:11.810 --> 19:14.270
It's just a small token
of our appreciation.

19:14.710 --> 19:16.320
Thank you. It's my honor.

19:16.610 --> 19:17.800
I won't disturb you any longer.

19:17.800 --> 19:19.400
Call me if you need anything.

19:19.400 --> 19:20.090
Thank you.

19:31.440 --> 19:32.170
Come in.

19:37.030 --> 19:37.720
Mr. Wei.

19:38.190 --> 19:39.820
Mr. Feng has promoted

19:39.850 --> 19:41.510
Xu Miyu to forewoman as you requested.

19:41.510 --> 19:43.030
The situation
with the former executive floor forewoman

19:43.030 --> 19:44.720
has also been handled properly.

19:44.720 --> 19:46.820
Tell him to keep a low profile these days.

19:46.820 --> 19:47.410
Okay.

19:50.310 --> 19:52.840
There's one more thing
I need to report to you.

19:53.240 --> 19:53.880
Go ahead.

19:54.070 --> 19:56.510
Mr. Ji Feng,
who you asked me to investigate last time,

19:56.510 --> 19:58.370
is a black card guest in our hotel.

19:58.720 --> 19:59.920
As for the executive floor incident
this time,

19:59.920 --> 20:03.650
he was the guest who used
black card privileges to make a complaint.

20:06.270 --> 20:07.400
Did he meet with the chairwoman?

20:07.400 --> 20:08.310
No, he didn't.

20:08.920 --> 20:10.780
But I've checked his background.

20:10.920 --> 20:12.960
Since he graduated
from Birmingham three years ago,

20:12.960 --> 20:15.510
he's been moving across
various countries and regions,

20:15.510 --> 20:18.910
working as a professional manager
to launch hotel business.

20:19.000 --> 20:21.360
Previously,
a rumor came out from the board,

20:21.360 --> 20:22.640
saying that they would
find a professional manager

20:22.640 --> 20:24.270
to take over the hotel management.

20:24.270 --> 20:26.000
At this time, he appeared at...

20:34.490 --> 20:37.100
[Wei Siyuan, In His Youth]

20:38.920 --> 20:40.160
Okay. I got it.

20:44.400 --> 20:46.130
You're quite smug, aren't you?

20:50.150 --> 20:52.790
Mr. Wei, what are you talking about?

21:00.970 --> 21:03.300
On what grounds could you steal my things?

21:07.200 --> 21:08.610
Keep a close eye on him for me.

21:08.610 --> 21:10.500
Report to me if anything happens.

21:10.750 --> 21:11.240
Okay.

21:11.310 --> 21:17.500
[Purong Hotel]

21:25.750 --> 21:26.960
What did I tell you?

21:27.400 --> 21:30.060
Making a comeback
is the main theme of your life.

21:30.200 --> 21:30.890
Cheers.

21:31.820 --> 21:32.410
Cheers.

21:35.630 --> 21:37.540
I still feel like I'm dreaming.

21:37.570 --> 21:40.030
In the morning,
they said they would fire me.

21:40.070 --> 21:41.270
But in the evening, inexplicably,

21:41.270 --> 21:42.700
they said
they would promote me to forewoman.

21:42.700 --> 21:44.750
Maybe that Black Card Ji's complaint

21:44.750 --> 21:46.000
really worked.

21:46.810 --> 21:48.340
You've met your lucky star.

21:48.690 --> 21:50.930
Can you go to any room

21:50.960 --> 21:52.220
on the executive floor

21:52.220 --> 21:54.440
and bring me a bottle of shampoo
from there?

21:54.440 --> 21:55.850
Can you guarantee

21:56.240 --> 21:57.510
this matter won't affect

21:57.510 --> 21:59.020
the hotel's normal services?

21:59.020 --> 22:00.430
Okay. Just rest assured.

22:01.270 --> 22:03.030
He's not my lucky star.

22:03.400 --> 22:04.880
He's the instigator.

22:05.890 --> 22:08.150
It sounds like there's a story behind it.

22:08.200 --> 22:10.000
Regarding this shampoo incident
I've told you,

22:10.000 --> 22:11.270
he was the one investigating it.

22:11.270 --> 22:13.270
I was just a scapegoat.

22:14.960 --> 22:16.730
Then your current situation

22:16.780 --> 22:18.380
is very easy to understand.

22:19.890 --> 22:21.720
Do you know that Black Card Ji?

22:21.800 --> 22:23.750
I've heard of him,
but I couldn't match the name to the face.

22:23.750 --> 22:25.030
It wasn't until last time,

22:25.030 --> 22:26.720
at Mr. Duan Jr.'s caviar banquet,

22:26.720 --> 22:28.030
that I saw him for the first time.

22:28.030 --> 22:30.680
He has always had a good reputation
in the industry.

22:30.680 --> 22:32.360
Nor has he had any dark history.

22:32.360 --> 22:33.920
If you want to learn about him,

22:33.920 --> 22:35.320
you can check his resume.

22:35.530 --> 22:37.530
I don't have time to learn about him.

22:38.000 --> 22:39.460
But lately, I've been thinking

22:39.460 --> 22:42.350
though some people seemed annoying to you,

22:42.750 --> 22:45.510
then they just saved you by chance.

22:45.720 --> 22:47.960
Some people seemed nice to you,

22:47.960 --> 22:49.810
but then they suddenly turned against you,

22:49.810 --> 22:51.010
becoming hypocrites

22:51.270 --> 22:53.590
and stabbing you in the back
while you were unaware of it.

22:53.590 --> 22:56.450
Now you know how dangerous
the workplace is, right?

22:57.240 --> 22:58.240
Let me tell you.

22:58.310 --> 23:00.680
Those guests on your executive floor

23:00.680 --> 23:01.920
are full of hidden talents.

23:01.920 --> 23:03.570
There are all kinds of people there.

23:03.570 --> 23:05.130
When some of them speak,

23:05.400 --> 23:07.660
even Wei Siyuan doesn't dare to disobey.

23:09.030 --> 23:10.920
Even if Black Card Ji had saved me,

23:11.550 --> 23:12.640
why do you think

23:12.640 --> 23:15.030
Mr. Feng promoted me to forewoman?

23:15.750 --> 23:18.140
In terms of seniority and ability,

23:18.370 --> 23:20.940
or youth and strength,
I'm not even qualified.

23:20.940 --> 23:22.960
Forewoman
isn't a very high-ranking position.

23:22.960 --> 23:25.410
We don't know yet
whether it's something good or bad.

23:25.410 --> 23:27.240
Let me
highlight the main points for you now.

23:27.240 --> 23:28.960
Xu Miyu, remember this.

23:29.070 --> 23:31.030
Not only are the guests
on your executive floor

23:31.030 --> 23:33.070
all quite influential,

23:33.130 --> 23:35.720
but your colleagues
are also not to be trifled with.

23:35.720 --> 23:37.510
Even though they might look young,

23:37.510 --> 23:39.680
their workplace experience

23:39.680 --> 23:41.240
is definitely more extensive than yours.

23:41.240 --> 23:43.240
I advise you to be mentally prepared.

23:43.240 --> 23:45.180
It won't be easy for you

23:45.330 --> 23:46.570
to make them respect you.

23:46.570 --> 23:48.980
I know it's not easy
to be their forewoman.

23:49.270 --> 23:51.790
But this is just the beginning.

23:52.030 --> 23:53.960
From now on, I'm going to

23:53.960 --> 23:56.720
learn how to use a manager's mindset
and perspective

23:56.720 --> 23:58.510
to look at the executive floor,

23:58.510 --> 23:59.510
the HSKP Department

23:59.510 --> 24:01.240
and even the entire Purong Hotel.

24:01.240 --> 24:03.680
I'd like to see
how far I can go in this place.

24:03.680 --> 24:06.680
Right! This is the Xu Miyu I know.

24:06.750 --> 24:08.510
Dealing with whatever happens to you

24:08.510 --> 24:10.110
and never taking a step back.

24:10.720 --> 24:12.310
I still remember when you were a kid,

24:12.310 --> 24:15.070
even though your stepfather
and mother treated you like that,

24:15.070 --> 24:17.000
I never saw you cry.

24:17.200 --> 24:19.510
And you always did things
better than your sister.

24:19.510 --> 24:21.790
I think since childhood, you've been

24:21.790 --> 24:24.320
a strong heroine
who can always turn the tide.

24:25.510 --> 24:25.970
Come on.

24:26.120 --> 24:28.390
Let's drink to your workplace debut.

24:36.440 --> 24:37.430
I'm back.

24:42.410 --> 24:43.300
Ke Wenxue.

24:43.960 --> 24:44.880
Why don't you ask about it?

24:44.880 --> 24:46.070
She's back now.

24:46.640 --> 24:47.640
Ask her directly.

24:47.640 --> 24:49.640
On what grounds
can she become the forewoman?

24:49.640 --> 24:50.970
I'd like to hear it, too.

24:58.720 --> 24:59.680
Ms. Xu.

25:00.160 --> 25:00.880
Qingping.

25:00.880 --> 25:02.200
Don't try to cozy up to me.

25:02.200 --> 25:03.880
If you have the guts,
tell everyone the truth.

25:03.880 --> 25:05.740
How did you become the forewoman?

25:08.400 --> 25:10.310
I was also very surprised
to hear this news.

25:10.310 --> 25:11.490
You're still pretending, huh?

25:11.490 --> 25:13.200
When Black Card Ji
cancelled your bad reviews,

25:13.200 --> 25:14.160
I could sense it.

25:14.160 --> 25:15.920
You have such a strong background.

25:15.920 --> 25:17.160
Since you have such a powerful backer,

25:17.160 --> 25:19.100
why are you here
to compete with us for the forewoman?

25:19.100 --> 25:20.350
You should go to the board and tell them

25:20.350 --> 25:21.510
to directly appoint you as the director.

25:21.510 --> 25:22.720
Isn't that even more awesome?

25:22.720 --> 25:23.680
Just like everyone else,

25:23.680 --> 25:25.160
I was hired by the hotel
through an interview.

25:25.160 --> 25:26.550
I don't have any backers.

25:26.550 --> 25:28.960
But since the hotel
has promoted me to forewoman,

25:28.960 --> 25:30.220
there must be a reason.

25:31.880 --> 25:34.080
Because of your three bad reviews, huh?

25:34.400 --> 25:35.680
Then I really couldn't catch up
in my whole life

25:35.680 --> 25:37.010
no matter how hard I try.

25:59.240 --> 26:00.030
Yin Xiang.

26:01.130 --> 26:02.170
Miyu.

26:03.270 --> 26:04.200
You look great

26:04.700 --> 26:07.630
in this outfit.

26:08.880 --> 26:10.270
Do you also think I...

26:10.270 --> 26:11.110
No, I don't.

26:11.590 --> 26:13.520
It's good to become the forewoman.

26:14.030 --> 26:16.990
Luo Qingping is unhappy

26:17.110 --> 26:20.040
because she thought
she could become the forewoman.

26:26.240 --> 26:28.030
It's fine. She's just like that.

26:28.030 --> 26:28.960
Just ignore her.

27:13.960 --> 27:16.720
Thank you all for coming to work on time.

27:20.790 --> 27:22.650
You're even thanking us for that?

27:23.110 --> 27:25.590
Then if I clean
more than a dozen rooms every day,

27:25.590 --> 27:28.590
you might even
have to give me an honorary banner, huh?

27:31.510 --> 27:33.570
Today's morning meeting is about...

27:33.680 --> 27:36.920
Then I'll sue them
for violating the Labor Contract Law!

27:37.680 --> 27:38.640
They notified me in the morning

27:38.640 --> 27:40.160
and asked me to leave in the afternoon.

27:40.160 --> 27:41.960
They didn't give me
a one-month notice in advance.

27:41.960 --> 27:44.400
Nor did they pay me double
for the last month.

27:44.400 --> 27:46.030
Mr. Lin, you are so lucky.

27:46.030 --> 27:47.680
The last sunlit guest room
on the executive floor

27:47.680 --> 27:49.010
just became available.

27:49.110 --> 27:51.160
Room 1812. It's all set.

27:49.920 --> 27:51.200
[Purong Hotel] [Resident Identity Card
of the People's Republic of China]

27:51.160 --> 27:52.550
The elevator is over there.

27:52.550 --> 27:54.030
I've worked in the company
for over 10 years.

27:54.030 --> 27:56.040
Can they just fire me so suddenly?

27:56.830 --> 27:58.890
How could they deal with it like this?

28:04.750 --> 28:07.580
[Weekly Shift Schedule
for Executive Floor Staff]

28:04.830 --> 28:06.790
Have you all
seen this week's shift schedule?

28:06.790 --> 28:07.660
Do you have any suggestions?

28:07.660 --> 28:09.510
A shift schedule is arranged so complexly.

28:09.510 --> 28:10.350
Just some superficial efforts.

28:10.350 --> 28:11.070
Exactly.

28:12.400 --> 28:13.160
Ms. Xu.

28:13.690 --> 28:14.410
Go ahead.

28:14.730 --> 28:16.260
I need to go to the restroom.

28:16.350 --> 28:17.160
Just go.

28:22.880 --> 28:23.680
Ke.

28:24.710 --> 28:25.770
Your mobile phone.

28:25.960 --> 28:27.310
Ms. Xu, someone made a complaint.

28:27.310 --> 28:28.110
I need to go deal with it.

28:28.110 --> 28:29.310
Go. Just go now.

28:31.750 --> 28:33.520
This regular meeting is held
in quite a democratic way.

28:33.520 --> 28:34.930
Isn't it a waste of time?

28:36.790 --> 28:37.590
Ms. Xu.

28:38.140 --> 28:40.270
I want to apply for five days
of compensatory leave

28:40.270 --> 28:41.270
to prepare for the exam.

28:41.270 --> 28:42.110
Five days?

28:42.790 --> 28:44.240
Isn't that too long?

28:44.550 --> 28:47.880
Previously, we only
had three consecutive days off at most.

28:48.000 --> 28:50.310
That's because
you haven't been here long enough, Ms. Xu.

28:50.310 --> 28:52.030
When Ms. Zhang was here,

28:52.350 --> 28:54.480
we could take more than three days off.

28:56.350 --> 28:58.510
Then I'll go back
and check your leave record.

28:58.510 --> 28:59.110
No need.

28:59.220 --> 29:00.640
Over the past three years,
I've accumulated

29:00.640 --> 29:01.550
27 days of compensatory leave,

29:01.550 --> 29:02.920
not even including
this year's annual leave.

29:02.920 --> 29:04.160
Not to mention taking five days off,

29:04.160 --> 29:05.820
I can even take five weeks off.

29:06.550 --> 29:08.290
Then when will you start your leave?

29:08.290 --> 29:09.180
Today.

29:11.110 --> 29:12.070
Today?

29:13.070 --> 29:14.750
There's a conference in our hotel now.

29:14.750 --> 29:16.310
The executive floor is fully booked.

29:16.310 --> 29:17.510
We are short-handed.

29:17.550 --> 29:18.960
Does that have anything to do with me?

29:18.960 --> 29:20.000
As a leader,

29:20.110 --> 29:21.310
you should have considered in advance

29:21.310 --> 29:22.750
the issue
of employees taking compensatory leave.

29:22.750 --> 29:24.950
Bargaining with your subordinates now

29:25.240 --> 29:26.440
shows no competence.

29:27.270 --> 29:29.510
I've rejected your application
of compensatory leave.

29:29.510 --> 29:31.310
Tell your parents to come next month.

29:31.310 --> 29:34.510
Drop everything this month
no matter how important it is.

29:36.430 --> 29:36.960
Alright.

29:37.430 --> 29:39.160
Then you can take five days off.

29:42.750 --> 29:44.240
Ms. Xu, I want to take a leave, too.

29:44.240 --> 29:45.640
If other employees want to take a leave,

29:45.640 --> 29:47.250
wait until Luo Qingping comes back.

29:47.250 --> 29:49.350
Why can she take a leave but I can't?

29:49.350 --> 29:51.240
She's preparing
for the Adult College Entrance Exam

29:51.240 --> 29:52.700
to change her own destiny.

29:52.820 --> 29:54.880
Does taking a stupid exam
make her superior?

29:54.880 --> 29:56.150
You just heard it, too.

29:56.510 --> 29:59.160
Luo Qingping has accumulated 27 days
of compensatory leave these three years,

29:59.160 --> 30:00.510
which means she has been working

30:00.510 --> 30:02.240
without any days off all year round,

30:02.240 --> 30:04.240
so it's reasonable for her
to take this leave.

30:04.240 --> 30:06.960
Gosh. What a double standard.

30:15.590 --> 30:17.750
Our hotel's employee handbook says

30:17.750 --> 30:20.350
two people on the same floor
can't take a leave at the same time,

30:20.350 --> 30:22.790
so I'm not making things difficult
for you all on purpose.

30:22.790 --> 30:24.750
Guys, please understand.

30:25.920 --> 30:26.430
Mi-

30:26.880 --> 30:28.340
Ms. Xu, come here quickly.

30:30.010 --> 30:30.930
Coming.

30:31.790 --> 30:33.320
That's all for the meeting.

30:33.830 --> 30:34.790
Miyu.

30:36.290 --> 30:37.050
Miyu.

30:37.950 --> 30:38.830
Go ahead.

30:40.030 --> 30:42.750
I'm sorry, Mr. Lin. I'm sorry.

30:42.750 --> 30:44.390
Are you playing tricks on me?

30:44.550 --> 30:46.210
The receptionist just told me

30:46.350 --> 30:48.410
there was only this sunlit room left.

30:48.550 --> 30:49.950
And now you're telling me

30:50.550 --> 30:52.280
to move to another sunlit room.

30:52.400 --> 30:53.480
How did you magically produce

30:53.480 --> 30:54.960
so many sunlit rooms?

30:55.110 --> 30:56.000
Was the receptionist lying to me

30:56.000 --> 30:57.030
or are you?

30:57.160 --> 30:58.750
Do I look gullible?

31:01.000 --> 31:02.670
I'm sorry, Mr. Lin.

31:03.310 --> 31:04.510
Please calm down.

31:04.550 --> 31:05.550
I can't calm down.

31:05.750 --> 31:07.680
Why isn't your forewoman here yet?

31:08.350 --> 31:09.510
I'll rush her.

31:12.550 --> 31:13.270
Yin Xiang.

31:13.550 --> 31:16.610
I will take your menstrual cramps
into consideration.

31:16.880 --> 31:17.790
How about this?

31:17.790 --> 31:19.920
I'll cover Luo Qingping's shift tonight.

31:19.920 --> 31:20.500
Really?

31:20.790 --> 31:21.790
Thank you, Miyu.

31:22.270 --> 31:24.450
Ms. Xu, where are you?

31:25.350 --> 31:26.000
Coming.

31:26.000 --> 31:27.000
Which room is it?

31:29.160 --> 31:31.110
You're lucky now.

31:31.110 --> 31:32.670
Someone's got your back.

31:33.640 --> 31:34.640
Speaking of Miyu,

31:34.750 --> 31:36.210
she's very easy to talk to.

31:46.560 --> 31:47.430
Ji...

31:50.110 --> 31:51.070
Mr. Ji.

31:51.160 --> 31:52.270
What are you doing here?

31:52.270 --> 31:54.270
Ask your forewoman to come here now.

31:54.350 --> 31:56.880
I'm the new forewoman
of the executive floor.

31:57.070 --> 31:58.510
You are the forewoman?

32:06.640 --> 32:07.690
What's going on?

32:07.750 --> 32:09.010
It's a double booking.

32:26.070 --> 32:27.350
Mr. Lin, right?

32:27.350 --> 32:28.640
I'm the forewoman of the executive floor.

32:28.640 --> 32:29.790
My name is Xu Miyu.

32:33.000 --> 32:33.790
Here's the thing.

32:33.790 --> 32:35.270
T-Today, our...

32:35.270 --> 32:36.750
Your computer is broken.

32:36.840 --> 32:38.840
She has said it eight times already.

32:39.160 --> 32:40.000
Do you think

32:40.000 --> 32:42.070
it's okay
if I arrange another room for you?

32:42.070 --> 32:43.240
It's not okay!

32:43.550 --> 32:44.880
Why should I give in?

32:45.400 --> 32:46.750
I gave in and then lost my job!

32:46.750 --> 32:48.790
Why do you still want me to give in?

32:48.960 --> 32:51.160
I've agreed
to transfer to another department.

32:51.160 --> 32:53.590
Why do they still insist on laying me off?

32:53.590 --> 32:56.270
Why am I always the one getting hurt?

32:56.270 --> 32:57.790
Am I just unlucky?

32:59.000 --> 33:00.790
I can understand how you feel.

33:01.440 --> 33:02.700
But here's the thing.

33:03.220 --> 33:04.830
This room has always been occupied

33:04.830 --> 33:06.000
by Mr. Ji,

33:06.000 --> 33:07.750
so I think for the sake of convenience...

33:07.750 --> 33:09.510
-Maybe it's still...
- What convenience?

33:09.510 --> 33:12.000
So "first come, first served"
also applies in checking into hotels, huh?

33:12.000 --> 33:14.350
Do I need to show you my resume?

33:14.350 --> 33:16.830
They said the ones who came first
surpassed me in seniority.

33:16.830 --> 33:18.830
And they said the ones who came later
were young and strong,

33:18.830 --> 33:20.590
being easier to order around than me.

33:20.590 --> 33:21.750
Let me tell you!

33:21.750 --> 33:23.350
I'm just staying here today!

33:23.510 --> 33:24.550
I just want this sunshine

33:24.550 --> 33:25.920
and this view!

33:25.920 --> 33:27.590
I've worked day and night
for over 10 years!

33:27.590 --> 33:30.310
I'm just going to enjoy my life properly!

33:32.550 --> 33:33.480
I'm just going to enjoy my life properly.

33:33.480 --> 33:34.200
Mr. Ji.

33:34.200 --> 33:35.440
I won't give in to anyone.

33:35.440 --> 33:36.310
From now on,

33:36.310 --> 33:37.200
I'll do whatever I want.

33:37.200 --> 33:38.440
Clean the room at once.

33:38.440 --> 33:40.350
Mr. Lin, welcome to our hotel.

33:40.370 --> 33:42.070
I'd like to apologize to you again.

33:42.070 --> 33:42.790
Mr. Ji.

33:44.790 --> 33:46.610
Mr. Ji, let me do it.

33:48.590 --> 33:51.350
I also want to thank you
for helping me keep my job.

33:54.510 --> 33:57.510
Your promotion to forewoman
has nothing to do with me.

33:58.130 --> 33:59.690
I also don't know what happened,

33:59.690 --> 34:01.760
but I know because of your complaint,

34:01.790 --> 34:04.200
the shampoo incident was exposed.

34:04.310 --> 34:06.650
And I've never told anyone else about it.

34:11.770 --> 34:13.030
I'm really sorry about today.

34:13.030 --> 34:14.800
Due to the mistake we made in our work,

34:14.800 --> 34:16.570
you have to change to another room.

34:16.570 --> 34:18.830
Thank you for cooperating with our work.

34:20.199 --> 34:20.920
Which room?

34:22.570 --> 34:23.790
1825.

34:25.179 --> 34:27.659
It's the one on the edge.

34:27.870 --> 34:29.010
That's an east-facing room,

34:29.010 --> 34:30.320
but it's without afternoon heat
from the setting sun.

34:30.320 --> 34:31.580
It's a prime location.

34:33.150 --> 34:35.090
Why don't you work as a saleswoman
in a real estate company?

34:35.090 --> 34:36.449
Prime location, huh?

34:38.190 --> 34:40.000
I'll bring the room card for you later

34:40.000 --> 34:41.530
along with a fruit platter.

34:41.960 --> 34:43.070
Once that gentleman moves out,

34:43.070 --> 34:44.880
we'll immediately arrange for you to move

34:44.880 --> 34:46.409
back to your previous room.

34:53.020 --> 34:54.060
Please come in.

35:00.000 --> 35:02.000
I didn't expect the shampoo incident

35:02.000 --> 35:03.060
would involve you.

35:03.210 --> 35:04.730
But luckily, you can keep your job now.

35:04.730 --> 35:05.990
We are even now, right?

35:15.270 --> 35:18.110
Ke, what exactly happened just now?

35:18.110 --> 35:19.780
Miyu, I'm sorry.

35:19.810 --> 35:20.620
That Black Card Ji...

35:20.620 --> 35:21.250
No...

35:21.280 --> 35:24.280
When Mr. Ji asked me
to handle the extension of his stay,

35:24.280 --> 35:26.000
I was busy with something else.

35:26.000 --> 35:28.260
Then I forgot to enter it into the system.

35:28.280 --> 35:30.550
How could you
forget such an important thing?

35:30.550 --> 35:32.670
Fortunately,
Mr. Ji took a step back just now.

35:32.670 --> 35:34.430
Otherwise,
what if the guest complained about us?

35:34.430 --> 35:36.710
Miyu, could you keep it a secret for me?

35:36.710 --> 35:38.550
Please. I promise
I won't make this mistake again.

35:38.550 --> 35:39.190
Please.

35:39.190 --> 35:40.320
Alright. Forget it.

35:40.390 --> 35:42.710
This matter ends here
as far as I'm concerned.

35:42.710 --> 35:44.030
But I have to warn you.

35:44.030 --> 35:45.070
You must never

35:45.070 --> 35:46.030
make such a mistake again.

35:46.030 --> 35:47.240
Thank you, Miyu.

35:47.280 --> 35:48.480
I promise
I'll never make this mistake again.

35:48.480 --> 35:49.550
You are truly an angel.

35:49.550 --> 35:50.360
Thank you.

35:58.850 --> 36:00.710
I've heard the famous Black Card Ji

36:00.710 --> 36:03.960
stood up for a female attendant
on the executive floor.

36:06.000 --> 36:07.360
You even heard of that?

36:08.400 --> 36:09.760
It looks like
Purong Hotel's biggest problem

36:09.760 --> 36:10.960
is being too gossipy.

36:11.360 --> 36:13.110
I've never made any gossip.

36:13.110 --> 36:14.960
I'm just a porter of gossip.

36:15.820 --> 36:16.960
Why couldn't I sense that

36:16.960 --> 36:19.220
you would show such kindness to a rookie?

36:19.510 --> 36:22.070
The HSKP Department
was reselling daily necessities,

36:22.070 --> 36:23.920
which involved an attendant.

36:23.920 --> 36:26.000
I was already investigating this clue,

36:26.000 --> 36:28.400
so I just helped her out.

36:29.070 --> 36:30.710
You just helped her out?

36:31.150 --> 36:34.030
Then you just
helped with her promotion to forewoman?

36:34.030 --> 36:36.110
I wasn't so capable...

36:38.150 --> 36:39.550
as to help an attendant who got

36:39.550 --> 36:41.760
all three bad reviews
in just one month of working here

36:41.760 --> 36:43.760
to promote to forewoman overnight.

36:44.070 --> 36:45.760
Is Purong's current promotion system

36:45.760 --> 36:46.960
really this chaotic?

36:48.320 --> 36:49.710
You're easily surprised
as you haven't seen much.

36:49.710 --> 36:51.000
This is nothing.

36:51.070 --> 36:53.550
At Purong Hotel,
that's just a piece of cake.

36:54.190 --> 36:55.960
Go take a look inside the hotel.

36:56.320 --> 36:58.110
There are stories
of confusing right and wrong.

36:58.110 --> 36:59.360
Their dramatic plots

36:59.360 --> 37:01.690
are completely beyond your imagination.

37:01.960 --> 37:02.760
In my opinion,

37:02.760 --> 37:04.090
what happened to Xu Miyu

37:04.400 --> 37:06.060
was at least not a farce.

37:06.230 --> 37:07.760
That's already quite good.

37:08.480 --> 37:09.590
Do you know Xu Miyu?

37:11.400 --> 37:13.930
I guess I'm the one
who discovered her talent.

37:14.480 --> 37:16.410
Were you the one who recruited her?

37:18.070 --> 37:19.590
I think she's pretty good.

37:20.710 --> 37:22.840
She's both beautiful and smart.

37:23.400 --> 37:24.590
It's just a pity that

37:24.590 --> 37:27.400
associating with these girls
in the HSKP Department

37:27.400 --> 37:28.710
is a bit of a waste of her talent

37:28.710 --> 37:30.230
and is holding her back.

37:30.630 --> 37:31.510
Ji Feng.

37:32.150 --> 37:33.360
If you're really determined

37:33.360 --> 37:35.400
to reorganize Purong Hotel,

37:35.400 --> 37:37.880
you must have your own people by your side
who you can trust

37:37.880 --> 37:39.360
and are also capable.

37:39.960 --> 37:42.110
Xu Miyu is a very suitable candidate.

37:43.550 --> 37:45.010
You think she's suitable?

37:47.150 --> 37:49.280
I think she's too weak in personality.

37:49.630 --> 37:51.850
She won't remain in the position
of forewoman for long.

37:51.850 --> 37:55.010
If I ask someone whose position
is precarious to be my trusted aide,

37:55.010 --> 37:56.270
what's the use of that?

37:59.360 --> 38:00.690
I think it's quite good.

38:23.570 --> 38:27.210
[REC]

38:37.550 --> 38:38.840
What happened?

38:39.550 --> 38:40.750
It hurts, doesn't it?

38:41.510 --> 38:42.400
It hurts, huh?

39:00.400 --> 39:01.570
Ke Wenxue, Ke Wenxue.

39:01.570 --> 39:03.300
Are you in charge of Corridor A?

39:03.710 --> 39:04.590
No, I'm not.

39:04.590 --> 39:05.710
I swapped with someone else.

39:05.710 --> 39:06.910
Who did you swap with?

39:07.550 --> 39:08.840
I also forgot.

39:09.590 --> 39:11.630
Why didn't you guys
follow the shift schedule?

39:11.630 --> 39:14.360
Things would get messed up easily
if you swap by yourselves like this.

39:14.360 --> 39:16.030
It's messy not because of me.

39:16.030 --> 39:17.000
As soon as Luo Qingping took a leave,

39:17.000 --> 39:18.860
everyone's shifts got messed up.

39:20.400 --> 39:21.590
Alright. I got it.

39:26.920 --> 39:28.360
Is anyone there?

39:28.360 --> 39:30.510
Someone in our room
is having an allergic reaction.

39:30.510 --> 39:32.510
Her neck is all swollen.

39:32.510 --> 39:33.510
Coming!

39:34.310 --> 39:35.310
What's wrong?

39:39.070 --> 39:40.070
Hurry up!

39:42.070 --> 39:42.960
Right here.

39:43.960 --> 39:44.630
It's so severe.

39:44.630 --> 39:45.840
I'll contact the receptionists

39:45.840 --> 39:47.360
and ask them
to bring some allergy medicine up here.

39:47.360 --> 39:48.110
Please wait a moment.

39:48.110 --> 39:48.960
Go at once.

39:48.960 --> 39:49.880
Hurry up.

39:51.230 --> 39:53.670
Today, it just feels so itchy.

39:54.030 --> 39:54.630
As a result...

39:54.630 --> 39:55.550
It's alright, Fang.

39:55.550 --> 39:56.400
It's alright.

39:56.960 --> 39:58.960
We've prepared so hard
for over half a year,

39:58.960 --> 40:01.960
but we didn't even make it
to the finals in the end.

40:02.070 --> 40:03.550
This is really...

40:06.150 --> 40:07.150
I'm sorry.

40:07.150 --> 40:08.590
The Front Office is really so busy.

40:08.590 --> 40:09.880
I'll go downstairs to get it right now

40:09.880 --> 40:10.800
and bring it up here immediately.

40:10.800 --> 40:11.710
Please wait a moment.

40:11.710 --> 40:13.030
Okay.

40:13.030 --> 40:13.590
Please hurry up.

40:13.590 --> 40:16.190
-Bring it here as soon as possible.
-Thank you.

40:16.780 --> 40:18.100
Don't cry.

40:20.070 --> 40:21.070
What is this for?

40:21.400 --> 40:22.030
In the past few days,

40:22.030 --> 40:23.400
her neck problem has relapsed.

40:23.400 --> 40:24.590
She can't sleep on a pillow,

40:24.590 --> 40:25.710
so she can only put a towel

40:25.710 --> 40:27.200
under her neck and sleep on it.

40:27.200 --> 40:27.920
In the past few days,

40:27.920 --> 40:30.400
Fang has really suffered a lot.

40:43.550 --> 40:44.400
Yin Xiang.

40:46.280 --> 40:48.150
We have an important guest
coming tomorrow.

40:48.150 --> 40:49.070
The room is already booked.

40:49.070 --> 40:50.070
It's Room 1818.

40:50.280 --> 40:51.860
Go clean it now.

40:52.000 --> 40:54.400
Miyu, why are you only telling me now?

40:55.000 --> 40:56.520
My shift is almost over.

40:56.840 --> 40:59.800
Don't you still have half an hour
before your shift ends?

40:59.800 --> 41:00.710
Half an hour.

41:01.030 --> 41:02.550
Just wait another half an hour.

41:02.550 --> 41:04.140
And then ask someone else to clean it.

41:04.140 --> 41:05.270
I'm leaving now.

41:09.280 --> 41:13.280
The guest in Room 1817 is complaining
about allergies caused by towels.

41:13.320 --> 41:14.450
I'll be right there.

41:16.800 --> 41:18.480
Why is it getting worse?

41:18.710 --> 41:20.800
Do you need me to contact the hospital?

41:20.800 --> 41:23.360
We're going to
the high-speed rail station soon.

41:23.360 --> 41:25.840
She can go to the hospital
after she gets home.

41:25.840 --> 41:28.490
But the towel issue
must be resolved first.

41:28.800 --> 41:29.510
You have to

41:29.510 --> 41:31.030
give us an explanation today.

41:31.030 --> 41:31.880
Yes.

41:31.880 --> 41:34.340
We can't leave
until this issue is resolved.

41:34.550 --> 41:35.550
Allergies to towels?

41:35.550 --> 41:36.800
Absolutely.

41:37.000 --> 41:40.000
Such a situation
has never happened to her before.

41:40.000 --> 41:41.360
But just in the past few days,

41:41.360 --> 41:43.150
after putting this towel from your hotel

41:43.150 --> 41:44.840
under her neck to sleep on it,

41:44.840 --> 41:45.710
she has gotten this allergic reaction.

41:45.710 --> 41:47.070
I'll go report this situation

41:47.070 --> 41:48.230
to our superiors right now.

41:48.230 --> 41:49.470
Please wait a moment.

41:49.840 --> 41:51.020
Okay. Please hurry up.

41:51.020 --> 41:52.050
We have a train to catch.

41:51.900 --> 41:54.190
[REC]

41:52.190 --> 41:53.510
Okay. I'll be right back.

41:53.510 --> 41:54.800
Please hurry up.

41:55.320 --> 41:57.400
This hotel is not okay.

41:57.480 --> 41:59.150
If it's really because of the towel,

41:59.150 --> 42:00.920
we need to ask them for compensation.
